#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `@RegisterForReflection` annotation instructs Quarkus to keep the class and its members during the native compilation. More details about the `@RegisterForReflection` annotation can be found on  the xref:writing-native-applications-tips.adoc#registerForReflection[native application tips] page."
msgstr "`@RegisterForReflection` 注解会指示 Quarkus 在本机编译过程中保留该类及其成员。有关 `@RegisterForReflection` 注解的更多详细信息，请参阅 xref:writing-native-applications-tips.adoc#registerForReflection[本机应用程序提示] 页面。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We use public fields here, but you can use private fields and getters/setters if you prefer."
msgstr "这里我们使用的是公共字段，但如果你愿意，也可以使用私有字段以及getter/setter方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This constructor will be used by Hibernate, and it must have a matching constructor with all the class attributes as parameters."
