#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The following examples are for the active record pattern, but the same can be used with repositories."
msgstr "以下示例针对的是Active Record模式，但同样适用于存储库。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "First: Locking using findById()."
msgstr "第一：使用 findById() 进行锁定。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Second: Locking in a find()."
msgstr "第二：在 find() 中进行锁定。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc
